text: Evan Comerford (born 1998) is a Gaelic footballer who plays for the Ballymun Kickhams club and at senior level for the Dublin county team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Ballymun Kickhams Gaelic footballers Category:DCU Gaelic footballers Category:Dublin inter-county Gaelic footballers Category:Gaelic football goalkeepers Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
